What is SessionFactory, how do we need to manage in an Hibernate application?
SessionFactory acts as an repository for holding configuration/mapping information with which it creates a ConnectionPool to optimize in creating the Session object

How many SessionFactory objects we need to create within an application?
1 SessionFactory = 1 application, per 1 database

How many Session objects we need to create in an application?
1 session object per 1 operation

Why we should not create multiple objects of the SessionFactory for a same database in an Hibernate application?
	

	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	